des: Sweet Spots SF provides ten tips for places to buy chocolates, ice creams, cakes and juices, five activities to do including where to hike and a few other nuggets for your time in the city. Whether you're in SF for a weekend or a week, there'll be something to discover and experience in this wonderful coastal city.
